Woot woot prom and senior breakfast are this friday!! I'm very excited!! But not at the same time I am pissed because we got lied to by the girl in charge of  our limo said that we had an escalade and just found out last week that it is just a regular stretch limo!!!! I cant believe it I had to pay $117 for that!!! My friend said that she got a hummer for $130 a person!!!

I hate it this is soo stressful and I am trying to stop smoking but this is very stressful ya know prom and graduation and all........ I really need to stop because I know its not good for you and I found out that one of my uncles has emphazema and another one just had like 4 heart attacks and they are still smoking!! So i need to stop before i become another statistic!!!

Well back to prom talk

Heres my schedual for friday:

  1. Wake up go to school.
  2. Go to 1st period
  3. go to senior breakfast
  4. Leave school
  5. go to ralphs
  6. Call Norha
  7. Have Norha do my hair
  8. Get dressed
  9. do make up
  10. take pictures
  11. go to prom and have fun

We really dont know what we are doing after prom yet..... how sad is that?? Its 2 days away and we have no idea what we are doing!! Ok well thats all for now!!!

You're a sweet girl, Jessica. And deep down, you're a great person. It's too bad people can't see it. The whole smoking, and partying, and sex stuff doesn't really help, but deep down you are great. I hope you and Jessica work everything out, because you guys were so close. I remember Jessica telling me how much her dad did for you. I hope you never took that for granted. Do good things and accomplish your goals. I had a crush on you for a reason. Stick to your morals and your friends. M.A.

Who ever wrote this I really appreciate it!! It was very sweet. Just to let you know I dont party anymore and even when I it wasnt like I was doing anything bad ya know? Yes I know I need to quit smokeing. And the whole sex thing its not like I go ariund having sex with everyone I am with one person and I have been with him for a year and a half!!! And we are safe about it !!! I dont know if you got the wrong idea when I said I have sex but i am with one person and I am 18 years old thats good there are girls that start having sex when they were 12 and 13 and sleep with like 30 guys!! So I think it is ver good that I was 17 and I am still with the same guy and I never did anything with anyone else besides kiss them!!! I hope me and Jess work everything out too!! I know her dad did everything for me I actually consider him more of a dad than my own!! I love him and miss him very much!!I never took anything he did for me for granted!!! Love

I found this survey on Lace's Journal so I'd thought I would try it!!!
 
 
deep survey
1. If you were to die this evening with no opportunity to communicate with anyone, what would you most regret not having told someone? I would regret not tellling my parents, my brother(rob),  my boyfriend, and Jess how much I really love them.


2. If a new medicine were developed that would cure arthritis but cause a fatal reaction in 1 percent of those who took it, would you want it to be released to the public? Only if they could find out who that 1 percent is thruogh tests and not give it to them.

3. If you were able to live to the age of 90 and retain either the body or the mind of a 30-year-old for the last 60 years of your life, which would you want? I would want to keep the body of a 30 year old unless I am a crazy old lady.....because I believe that your mind stays with you no matter how old you get.

4. If at birth you could select the profession your child would eventually pursue, would you do so? No because I would probably change my mind.


5. If you knew there would be a nuclear war in one week, what would you do? I would say goodbye to everyone and tell them that I love them all and you know who you are!!! I would bugee jump, go skydiving,spend all my money on senseless stuff probably put myself in debt!!, eat all the food i wanted cuz I wouldnt have to worry about getting fat, get married to ralph!!, and thats about it.

6. Would you accept twenty years of extraordinary happiness and fulfilment if it meant you had to die at the end of the period? No because it wouldnt be normal you have to have both ups and downs in your life.

 



7. If the person you were engaged to marry had an accident and became a paraplegic, would you go through with the marriage or back out of it? I would definitly go through with it because I truely love the person.

 

 


8. Someone very close to you is in pain, paralysed, and will die in a month. Would you poison them if they begged you to? No I would not be able to live with myself after that...I would probably kill mysekf afetr doing that!!

 

 


9. What is the worst psychological torture you can imagine suffering? (it cannot involve any physical harm to you) Ralph leaving me!! I dont think I would be able to live anymore.

10. You and a person you love deeply are placed in separate rooms with a button next to each of you. You know that you will both be killed unless one of you presses the button before 60 minutes pass; furthermore, the first to press the button will save the other person, but will immediately be killed. What do you think you would do? I would push the button.. gonna die anyway.. and I dont wanna live without them.

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 


11. Would you be willing to go to a slaughterhouse and kill a cow? No way in hell!!!!!


 

 

12. For $20,000 would you go for 3 months without washing, brushing your teeth, or using deodorant? (You can't tell anyone that you're getting paid) Ewwww no way!!

 

 

 

13. Which of these restrictions could you best tolerate: leaving the country permanently or never leaving the state in which you now live? ummmm I dont know cuz i dont want to leave the coutry but I def want to leave new york its way too expensive here!!!

 

 

 



14. If you could choose the sex and physical appearance of your soon-to-be-born child, would you do it? NO they should come out how they are supposed to!!

15. Would you be willing to decrease your life expectancy by 5 years if you could become extremely attractive? NO!!!!

 

 

 

 

 

16. If your friends and acquaintances were willing to bluntly tell you what they really think of you, would you want them to? Yes. So then i know who my true friends are.


. Would it disturb you much if, upon your death, your body were simply thrown into the woods and left to rot? No, it would disturb me more if they shake and bake me, put me in an urn and put me on their table.. now THATS a weird custom we have.


18. Would you like to know the precise date of your death? Yes... i would wanna know to live it up until then.


19. Would you be willing to give up all television for the next 5 years if it would induce for someone to provide for 1,000 starving children in Indonesia? Yes... for sure. Just dont take my radio too.


Those were definitly deep questions!!!

This is when the bad stuff starts happening!!! Dun dun dun!!

We went home to take the tire off and put the doghnut on but the f-ing tire would not come off it took from 9pm to 12 am to get the tire off!!! So we went back to see what I hit and guess what it was a doughnut!!!! You could see the dirt marks from where I hit it!! I was sooo pissed cuz now I have to drive on a doughnut til thursday!!!!!

Well thats it for now no more exciting tire blow outs!!!!!

" In This Diary "


Here in this diary,
I write you visions of my summer.
It was the best I ever had.
There were choruses and sing-alongs,
and not a spoken feeling.
I'm knowing that right now is all that matters.
All the nights we stayed up talking
and listening to 80's songs;
quoting lines from all those movies that we love.
It still brings a smile to my face.
I guess when it comes down to it...

Being grown up isn't half as fun as growing up:
These are the best days of our lives.
The only thing that matters
is just following your heart
and eventually you'll finally get it right.

Breaking into hotel swimming pools,
and wreaking havoc on our world.
Hanging out at truck stops just to pass the time.
The black top's singing me to sleep.
Lighting fireworks in parking lots,
illuminate the blackest nights.
Cherry cokes under this moonlight summer sky.
2015 Riverside, it's time to say, "goodbye."
Get on the bus, it's time to go.

Being grown up isn't half as fun as growing up:
These are the best days of our lives.
The only thing that matters
is just following your heart,
and eventually you'll finally get it right.
